title: Tru-Ray Construction Paper P103031, 10 Classic Colors, 9" x 12", 50 Sheets
description: Teachers choose Tru-Ray construction paper for its durability and great assortment of bright, fade-resistant colors. They count on the Tru-Ray brand for unique, time-saving products such as the color wheel construction paper assortment, construction paper pads, and the Smart-Stack construction paper for presorted color assortments.
